Sessionapi

GET http://localhost:8080/sessions/api/today
returns the sessions that take place today

Menuapi

GET: http://localhost:8000/menu/api
Returns the menu of the day
--------------------------------------------------------

POST: http://localhost:8000/menu/api
Sets the menu of the day
-------------------------------------------------------

POST: http://localhost:8000/menu/api/find-sandwich
Finds a sandwich in the database by name using a sandwichRequestBodyDTO
-------------------------------------------------------

GET: http://localhost:8000/menu/api/find-sandwich/{id}
Finds a sandwich in the database by its id
-------------------------------------------------------

POST: http://localhost:8000/menu/api/sandwiches
Adds a sandwich to database using a sandwichcreationDTO
-------------------------------------------------------

PATCH: http://localhost:8000/menu/api/sandwiches/change-price/{id}
Updates the price of a sandwich using price requestbody and finding the sandwich by id
-------------------------------------------------------

PATCH : http://localhost:8000/menu/api/sandwiches/change-ingredients/{id}
Updates the ingredients of a sandwich using ingredientsDTO requestbody and finding the sandwich by id
-------------------------------------------------------

DELETE : http://localhost:8000/menu/api/sandwiches/{id}
Finds the sandwich by their id and deletes it from the database
